[section#basic.scope.lambda
    [:en] Lambda scope
    [:zh_CN] lambda 作用域
]

[para]
[:en]
A [~lambda-expression] [`E] introduces a [+:adj lambda[!scope]] that starts
immediately after the [~lambda-introducer] of [`E] and extends to the end of the
[~compound-statement] of [`E].
[:zh_CN]
[~lambda-表达式] [`E] 引入一个 [+:adj lambda[!作用域]]，开始于紧跟 [`E] 的
[~lambda-引导符] 之后，扩展到 [`E] 的[~复合语句]末尾。
